message: "If you use this dataset or code, please cite the T2KNOW corpus release and the associated paper."
title: "T2KNOW: A Huntington's Disease Literature Corpus for Nested and Same-Span Multi-Label Biomedical Named Entity Recognition"
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-05-08"
url: "https://github.com/edugredu/T2KNOWcorpusRelease"
